137
00:11:04,997 --> 00:11:05,873
No.

138
00:11:06,582 --> 00:11:07,750
Estoy aquí de compras.

139
00:11:07,833 --> 00:11:09,502
Pues compra.

140
00:11:21,013 --> 00:11:22,014
Vaya.

141
00:11:22,848 --> 00:11:23,682
¿Y estas?

142
